snippet.title: The Soul of Wind
snippet.description:
The Soul of Wind is music label for a large variety of Music. We provide the best services to the pianist, musician, artist. 
We always welcome you to join our music label! 

▬▬▬▬

For Audience: 
- Our Channel is A Wonderland for Beautiful Piano Music, Relaxing Music, Anime Music, Fantasy RPG, New Age Music . . . ( (also other type of music). ) 
- Listening and feeling ^^. Becoming a part of Dream land.

▬▬▬▬

For Artists:

►Distribution:
- For Release your music on music platform: Itunes, Spotify, Amazon . . . 
  Please Contact Us at: admin@thesoulofwind.com


►Music Promotion:
 If you want to submit a request to promote your music on our channel :
- Send us a mail at: admin@thesoulofwind.com
- Contact us on the facebook 

▬▬▬▬

Feel free to contact us if anything is wrong:
- Adding any kind of information which belongs to a the video we've uploaded (missing information of the music or visual.)


© 2020 The Soul of Wind
